# Upper Body [Strength Training] (2026-03-10 17:00-18:15) @RIR 2
@ location: Downtown Gym
@ focus: Hypertrophy — chest and back

> Last set of bench was RPE 9. Add 2.5kg next week.
> Solid session. Bench felt smooth, pull-ups getting stronger.

- Bench Press 4x8rep @80% 1RM bench press @rest 2min
  @ tempo: 30X1
- superset 3x:
  - Dumbbell Row 10rep @32kg @rest 60s
    @ unilateral: true
  - Incline Dumbbell Bench Press 10rep @28kg @rest 60s
- Pull-Up 3xmaxrep @bodyweight + 10kg @rest 90s
- superset 3x:
  - Cable Face Pull 15rep @RPE 7 @rest 45s
  - Lateral Raise 12rep @10kg @RIR 3 @rest 45s
- Triceps Pushdown 3x15rep @RPE 8 @rest 60s
